      "experience_key": "workflow--task7e-moveit-servo--startup-gates-before-motion",
      "title": "Task7E MoveIt Servo 启动应先串联状态门闩再允许运动",
      "summary": "在本仓库的 UR3 + MoveIt Servo fake hardware 链路里，稳定顺序是先等 /joint_states 与 forward_position_controller，再等 /servo_node/status，随后 commander 进入 idle ready，最后通过 Trigger 服务手动触发一轮短时 Twist。这样能把底层状态、Servo 初始化和运动命令失败分开定位。",
      "experience_type": "workflow",
